Detailed Description

Equals to spirit:addressBlock element in IP-Xact specification.

The AddressBlock describes a single contiguous block of memory that is part of a memory map. AddressBlock is a generalization of a class MemoryMapItem which is also the base class for classes Bank and SubspaceMap.
